page.title: 12M25 Motorway Traffic Count
page.content: A small group of children visited Clement St bridge to carry out a traffic count.Time-Monday afternoon between 2-3pm. RESULTS:Due north to Dartford. Time| Cars in|Middle lane|Fast lane|Not |slow lane| | |cars 1m | 7 | 2 | 9 | 9 2m | 11 | 10 | 11 | 12 4m | 30 | 30 | 36 | 30 RESULTS:Due north to Swanley. Time|S.lane|Midd.lane|F.lane|Not cars 1m | 11 | 7 | 3 | 6 3m | 25 | 16 | 3 | 12 10m | 90 | 129 | 20 | 130 The children concluded the motorway was very busy,the second lane was used the most,and there was a high proportion of vehicles other than cars- usually lorries.
